title: TurboTax Super Bowl Commercial 2017: 'Humpty Dumpty in the Hospital'
text:
The TurboTax commercial featuring Humpty Dumpty in the hospital is definitely one of the funniest ones we have seen so far during the 2017 Super Bowl and you can watch the spot right here!
The commercial features Humpty in the hospital after falling and using TurboTax to find out if he can get a tax deduction for his hospital stay.
There is also a first part to the commercial that debuted a couple of weeks ago and you can watch that video here.
Watch below!

TurboTax 2017 Big Game Commercial “Humpty Hospital” Click inside to watch the first part of the commercial…
